another. Black gives up his best piece, the knight, in order to eliminate the
defender of the c3- and e3-squares. After that, he manages do dominate in the
c-line and to win the game.} Nc2 29. Ra2 Nxe1+ 30. Rxe1 Rc3 31. Rae2 Rxd3+ 32.
